node.text:
We're committed to championing, supporting, and celebrating the LGBTQIA+ community—including our associates who embrace their beautifully varied identities.
 
Thanks for celebrating Pride with us! We’re proud to support LGBTQIA+ communities and organizations and we’re committed to continuing to lift and empower their voices today and every day.
 
📸: @victoriassecret

node.text:
Meet the talented individuals behind PINK With Purpose Project Winner @officialcocoadiaries: Dnai Thomas, Maleigha Cooper, Mariah Cooper, Kalani Franklin & Regan Nesbit🥇

"My co-founders and I have been close friends since middle school and we wanted to do something that would bring us together as friends as we went off to college since we were in different spaces. After brainstorming, we decided to create a platform for Black women in college.”

Head to our Story to learn more about them!

node.text:
Meet Bella and Myles from @coconutwhisk - one of our PINK With Purpose Project winners! 🏆

"Myles and I got started with Coconut Whisk in our small college apartment in 2018 after realizing that there weren’t any better-for-you, vegan & gluten-free baking mixes—so we created our own specialty blend, started selling them at farmer’s markets and the rest is history!"

👀 our Story to learn more about them!
